00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:59,810
Speaker 0: See, I used to feel that way, but when I went to Katsucon, even though the hotel room was expensive, I'd gone to so many cons where I overstuffed the room, it was real nice to share a room with just two other guys.

285
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:00,417
Speaker 1: Oh, yeah.

286
00:22:01,853 --> 00:22:02,955
Speaker 0: I paid out the ass for it.

287
00:22:04,137 --> 00:22:09,910
Speaker 0: But basically, there's a list of things and tricks that you have to do, because the hotel knows you're overstuffing.

288
00:22:10,270 --> 00:22:14,357
Speaker 0: Don't think for a second that they don't know exactly what you're planning, especially if you're at a con.

289
00:22:14,858 --> 00:22:21,490
Speaker 0: The thing is, they won't screw you, and they won't go out of their way to find you out, unless you really give them a hard time.

290
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:24,633
Speaker 0: So, it's kind of an open secret.

291
00:22:25,475 --> 00:22:33,770
Speaker 0: The rule number one, everyone must bring their own towels, because if you get a room that has an occupancy of four people, it's gonna have four towels in it.

292
00:22:34,751 --> 00:22:38,290
Speaker 0: If you request, you know, eight more towels, they're gonna be suspicious.

293
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:49,670
