00:59:06,060 --> 00:59:12,260
Speaker 0: Basically, first of all, we've got to talk about how to leave the con, which is actually more complicated than you'd think.

850
00:59:13,841 --> 00:59:15,244
Speaker 0: You'd be surprised.

